org.opendaylight.controller.sal.core

Class NodeConnector

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opendaylight.controller.sal.core.NodeConnector
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class NodeConnector
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Describe a generic network element attachment points, attached to one Node, the NodeConnector is formed by the pair (NodeConnectorType, NodeConnectorID) because each SDN technology can identify an attachment point on the Node in different way.
